column5: I understand that this business has been sold. We have been buying bait at this shop for years and would appreciate any information if anybody has dealt with the new owners and what they think about them. Thanks kindly for any reports
It's changed a bit. You can send me a pm for further info.

Purchased leeches there last July and they were just fine. Full pound and while size was mixed, overall good size. At the time, it looked as if the shop was mostly empty and the new owners were just taking over.
